// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3359 — Mass File Rename (blacksuit)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 806033bc-fa78-55fe-8876-6901ea86e781

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
